setup:
```sh
chezmoi init git@github.com:m1sk9/dotfiles.git
chezmoi apply
```

using:

- Browser: Mozilla Firefox Nightly
- Email Client: Mozilla Thunderbird Daily
- Terminal: Alacritty
- Shell: Fish
- Editor: Visual Studio Code, Zed, NeoVim
- IDE: JetBrains IDE
- Other:
    - DNS: NextDNS
    - VPN: Tailscale
    - Password Manager: 1Password
    - Music: Spotify
- PC:
    - Laptop (Main): MacBook Air M2 2022 (macOS Sonoma, 13.6-inch, 16GB RAM, 512GB SSD)
    - Desktop: self-created (Windows 11, Ryzen 5 5600X + GTX 1660 Super, 16GB RAM)
